🔷 BIAS–VARIANCE TRADEOFF
Problem	Meaning
High Bias	Underfitting
High Variance	Overfitting

Solution:

Regularization

More data

Cross-validation

🔷 REGULARIZATION

L1 (Lasso) → Feature selection

L2 (Ridge) → Prevent large weights

🔷 CROSS-VALIDATION

👉 Splitting data multiple times

Example:

K-Fold Cross Validation

🔷 HYPERPARAMETER TUNING

GridSearchCV

RandomSearchCV

